## Personalized Dashboard Layouts

### Adaptive UI Based on Segment

**Fearful Executor (checks dashboard constantly):**
- Emphasize calm: "Everything is under control"
- Hide rejected trades (creates anxiety)
- Show: Current positions, stops, regime (minimal, calm)

**Override Prone (frequently uses kill switch):**
- Emphasize protection: "System blocked 12 trades this month"
- Show: Rejected trades log, discipline streak, loss avoidance savings
- Warn early: "Daily loss at -0.8% (kill switch at -3%)"

**Options Focused (70%+ covered calls):**
- Emphasize income: "Premium collected this month: $2,400"
- Show: Options positions at top, roll scheduler, upcoming expirations
- Hide: Short equity signals (not their style)

**Implementation:**

```typescript
// app/institutional/page.tsx

const layout = getLayoutForSegment(data.user.behaviorSegment);

return (
  <div className="dashboard">
    {layout.showRejectedTrades && <RejectedTradesCard />}
    {layout.emphasizeOptions && <OptionsIncomeCard />}
    {layout.showDisciplineStreak && <DisciplineStreakCard />}
    {/* Standard cards for everyone */}
    <PositionsCard />
    <RegimeCard />
  </div>
);
```

