## Personalized Notifications

### Fogg's Prompt Timing

The **right message at the wrong time** is ignored. The **right message at the right time** drives action.

**Winzinvest notification strategy:**

| Time | Segment | Message |
|---|---|---|
| **7:00 AM** | All | Pre-market screener results (if signals found) |
| **9:25 AM** | Override Prone | "System is ready. You don't need to do anything." (calm anchor) |
| **11:00 AM** | Fearful Executor | "Mid-day check-in: All stops in place." (reassurance) |
| **3:55 PM** | Options Focused | "2 covered calls hit 80% decay — rolled automatically" |
| **After close** | All | Daily summary (P&L, trades, rejected setups) |

**Anti-pattern:**
- ❌ "TSLA up 5% — trade now!" (creates urgency to trade)
- ✅ "TSLA crossed your watchlist threshold — queued for tomorrow's open" (calm, systematic)

**Implementation:**
- Store notification preferences in `User` table: `notificationSegment`, `emailFrequency`, `telegramEnabled`
- Send via time-based scheduler (APScheduler on backend)
- Personalize content based on `behaviorSegment`

