## Progress Visualization (Development & Accomplishment)

### Show Trajectory, Not Just Current State

**Traditional dashboard:** "Net P&L: +$12,000"  
**Progress-aware dashboard:** "Net P&L: +$12,000 (up from +$8,000 last month) — 50% growth"

**Implementation:**

```typescript
<ProgressChart
  title="Your Discipline Over Time"
  metrics={[
    { label: 'Stop overrides', trend: 'down', current: 2, vs30d: 8 },
    { label: 'Trades taken', trend: 'stable', current: 15, vs30d: 14 },
    { label: 'Win rate', trend: 'up', current: 68, vs30d: 54 },
  ]}
/>
```

**Why this works:**
- Satisfies Development & Accomplishment (Core Drive 2)
- Shows user they're **improving** (not just performing)
- Reinforces discipline behavior (overrides going down = success)

